trans-unit.source: Prevents the [Ildasm.exe (IL Disassembler)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) from disassembling an assembly.
trans-unit.target: Impede o [Ildasm.exe (IL Disassembler)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) de desagregação de uma assemblagem.
Esta classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Runtime.CompilerServices.SuppressIldasmAttribute"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Runtime.CompilerServices.SuppressIldasmAttribute"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Apply the <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.SuppressIldasmAttribute> attribute to an assembly or module to prevent the assembly or module from being disassembled using the [Ildasm.exe (IL Disassembler)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Aplicar o <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.SuppressIldasmAttribute>atributo para uma assemblagem ou módulo para impedir que a assemblagem ou módulo que está a ser disassembled utilizando o [Ildasm.exe (IL Disassembler)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.SuppressIldasmAttribute>
